  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "NSB becomes Most Popular Banking & Finance Website for second consecutive year",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "The corporate website of NSB (www.nsb.lk) was awarded the Most Popular Banking & Finance website along with the merit award for Best Banking & Finance website at BestWeb.lk awards ceremony organized by LK Domain Registry on 30th of August 2022 at the Cinnamon Grand.",
        "www.nsb.lk has been continuously recognized and rewarded for its performance and this is the second consecutive year of NSB being ranked the most popular Banking & Finance website. Further to that, the website has been recognized as the best Sri Lankan website in 2020.",
        "The award was received by the Chairperson of NSB Keasila Jayawardane, GM/CEO of NSB- Ajith Peiris, Directors- Jayantha Perera, Lakshman Gamini and the Senior DGM- K. Raveendran. The event was honored by the participation of members of the corporate management of NSB.",
        "A strong international support base for Sri Lanka to get assurances from its creditors",
        "JICA launches three-year technical cooperation project with SLCG on oil spill response capability improvement",
